\id EPH - Kuna, San Blas - Bible -Panama 2014 (DBL -2014)
\h Efesios
\toc1 Éfeso-Dulemarse-Narmaklesad-Garda
\toc2 Efesios
\toc3 Ef
\mt1 ÉFESO-DULEMARSE-NARMAKLESAD-GARDA
\mt2 EFESIOS
\imt2 GEBE-SOGLENAID
\imt1 Garda-nug
\ip Pablo Bab-Burba-Isligwaledbali gwenadgan-Éfesoʼgi-bukmaladga garda narmaksad. Pablo esgaryagi Roma-neggweburgi-mellesigu, gardamar matabake narmaksad: Gálatas, Efesios, Filipenses, degi, Colosenses.
\ip Pablo Éfeso-neggweburgi birgapaa dulemar-odurdakmai gusad (Gusmalad 19). Éfeso-neggwebur Asia-yargi bur baiganba neggwebur-dummadga siid, Éfeso-neggweburse warmakmalaga, igar-nuegan-walabo maibalid. Degine, ur-nagumalad-nuegan nikbalid. Degine, Éfeso-akar Bab-Dummad-Gayaburba-Nued mimilesgusbalid.
\ip Binsamardo, we-garda birga 60ʼgi narmakles-insaye.
\is1 Éfeso-Dulemarse-Narmaklesad-Gardagi weyob sunmaklenaid
\ip Pablo gwenadgan-Éfesoʼgi bukmaladga sogsad, Bab-Dummad amba yoo we-napneg-nasiked-idu bato igar mesisye. Judíoʼmar, degine, Judíoʼsurmalad-Bab-Jesús-abingasmaladi, Jesucristoʼgi wargwennagwadga gunonidamarye. Pablo sogsabalid, bulakwaa arbamarye, degine, sogsabalid, anmar Bab-Dummad-neggi bela Bab-Jesucristoʼba ibmar-nikuoye.
\ip We-gardagine, weyob ilemakar sunmaklenaid:
\io1 1. Gebe-sikwas-soglenaid (1:1-2).
\io1 2. Bab-Dummadgi-abonoleged-igar (1:3–3:21).
\io1 3. Bab-Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-e-daed (4:1–6:20).
\io1 4. Napi-soglenaid (6:21-24).
\ip Be itogua.
\c 1
\ms1 1. GEBE-SIKWAS-SOGLENAID
\mr (1:1-2)
\p 
\v 1 Ani Pablo, an Bab-Dummad-sogedba Bab-Jesucristo-e-sapin-bur-dummadga gumogadid. Bemar-Jesucristoʼgi-akananaimaladga, gwenadgan-Éfesoʼgi Cristo-Jesúsʼgi-gwen-galakudisurmaladga, an garda barmisiid.
\p 
\v 2 Bab-Dummad anmar-baba, degi, anmar-Dummad-Jesucristo, bemargi nued binsamarsun, degi, ulubgi bogidik bemar-itogega imakbarsun.
\ms1 2. BAB-DUMMADGI-ABONOLEGED-IGAR
\mr (1:3–3:21)
\s1 Bab-Dummad Jesucristoʼgi anmar-susad
\p 
\v 3 Bab-Dummad, anmar-Dummad-Jesucristo-e-Bab, a-e-nug anmar odummomarsun. Ar anmargi nued binsasad, bela ibmar-nuegan nibneggi-ibmar-burbarmalad-bukmalad Cristoʼgi anmarga uksad.
\p 
\v 4 Amba yoo we-napneg-nagued-idu, Bab-Dummad, bato Cristoʼgi anmar-susad. Adi, anmar Bab-Dummadgadga guegar, degi, bela anmar dule-gwage-swilidikidga e-asabin gumalagar.
\v 5 Bab-Dummad anmar-sabedba Jesucristoʼgi-e-mimmiganga-anmar-imakega, iduar bato anmar-susad. Ar ade, Bab-Dummad na yeer-itogedba, na e-sogedba deyob anmar-susad.
\v 6 Adi, anmar Bab-Dummad-nug ogannogegar. Ar ade, Bab-Dummad e-mimmiganga anmar-imake-wilubsulinad, emigindi, na E-Machi-sabesailadba e-mimmiganga anmar-imaknonikid.
\p 
\v 7 Ar Jesucristo-ablis-aryosadgi, anmar isguedgi ollorgunonikid. Anmar isgussuliyob gunonisunnad. Bab-Dummad nabir anmargi binsaewilubsulinad, emigindi, bela-bela nabir-anmargi-binsaedba anmarga sognonisunnad: “Be-isgued bato bergussunye.”
\v 8 Ar Bab-Dummad na e-sabgued bela-bela anmarse oyosad. Bela ibmar nue-wisi-guega, degine, mag-ibmar-itogega anmar-imaknonikid.
\p 
\v 9 Deyob Bab-Dummad, Cristoʼgi bato dikasurgus na e-ibmar-saoye-sogsad-odukuar-maid, na e-itogedba anmarga odalononisunnad.
\v 10 Adi, Bab-Dummad na-ibmar-imakoed-ibagan-nonikile, bela ibmar nibneggi-bukmalad, degi, ibmar-napneggi-bukmalad, Cristoʼgi atononikoed.
\p 
\v 11 Bab-Dummad na e-itolegedba ibmar-sabied-imakedba iduar Cristoʼgi anmar-susad, adi, Cristoʼba anmar ibmar nikumalagar.
\v 12 Ar adi, anmar-inse Cristo-bengussurmalad-ulale, Bab-Dummad-gangued-e-nug anmargi-odummoledii guegar.
\p 
\v 13 Bemar ambamogad. Bemar, Bab-Dummad-Gayaburba-Nued Bab-Jesús-sunna-dule-abonoged, a-gayaburba be itosmargu, we-gayaburba-napiragwad be abingasmarmogad. Agi, bemar Cristoʼgi bensur-gunonimargu, Bab-Dummad-Burba-Isligwaled anmarga-uklegoye-sogsad, bemargi e-wilub nagunonisunnad, adi, oyogega, bemar Cristoʼgad-sunnadye.
\v 14 Bab-Dummad anmarga E-Burba-Isligwaled-uksadba bato anmarga sognaid, ibmar-nuegan-baigan anmarga-ukoye-sogsad anmarga bela ukedseye. Bab-Dummad bela dulemar-egadga-guoye-sogsad isguedgi-onosale, bela anmarga ibmar ukoed. Agi, Bab-Dummad-nug bela-bela ogannoledii guoed.
\s1 Pablo, Jesúsʼba-nanaimaladga Bab-Dummadse goled
\p 
\v 15 An bemar-itoardo, bemar Bab-Jesúsʼgi nue bensurmarye, degine, bemar bela Jesucristoʼgi-akananaimalad nue-sabmarbarye.
\v 16 Deyob an itoargu, an bemarga Bab-Dummadga-dog-nuedye-soged gwen an bogigudisulid. Bab-Dummadse an goter, bemargi an binsaddaed.
\p 
\v 17 Anmar-Dummad-Jesucristo-e-Bab-Dummad, Bab-Gandikid-Yeerdakleged, ase an bemarga egisdaed, bemarga ibmar-burbar-mag-itoged ukegar, adi, bemar mag itogegar, doa Bab-Dummad-gue.
\v 18 Bab-Dummadse an egisbar, ulubse ise mag-ibmar-itogega bemar-imakye, adi, bemar bur bule wisguega, ibiyobi Bab-Dummad ibmar-yoedse-ukoye-sogsad dummarba gue, degi, ibiyobi yeerdaklebali. We-ibmar, Bab-Dummad, e-sordaganga sabos siid.
\v 19 Degine, bemar wisguegarbar, Bab-Dummad-e-gangued ibibayobi-gannarba, degi, sogedba anmar-Bab-Jesúsʼgi-bensurmaladga ibmar-imake.
\p 
\v 20 We-gangued-gannarbagwadba, Cristo burgwar-maigu, Bab-Dummad gannar Cristo-odulosad. Agine, Bab-Dummad, Cristo Dummadga-guega nibneggi e-argan-nuedsik Cristo-sinonisunnad.
\p 
\v 21 We-ganguedbali, Bab-Dummad, Cristoʼgala bela burbamar-gargangued-nikamalad-birgi, degi, burbarmar-negsemamaid-birgi, bur bule dule-dummadga-guega imaksad.
\p Degine, we-ibagangi dummaganga-mamaid-birgi, degi, ibagan-binid-danikoedgi dummaganga-gumaloed-birgi, Jesús bur-dummadga nugsalesad.
\p 
\v 22 Bab-Dummad belagwapa Cristo-urbali ibmar urbisad. Degine, Bab-Dummad, Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-danar-ambikunonidamalad-e-sailaga, Cristo-nug-imaksabalid.
\p 
\v 23 Degisoggu, Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-danar-ambikunonidamalad-belagwapa Cristo-e-sanyobsundo.
\p Degine, Cristo, bela amar-e-ganguedid.
\p Cristoʼgi bela Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad dogar siid. Gwen Cristoʼgi ibmar galakudeeye soglesulid.
\c 2
\s1 Bab-Dummad, anmar-abonoge-wilubsulinad
\p 
\v 1 Bab-Dummad bemar-odulononikid deun, bemar galagwensuli-gudimargu, degi, be-isguedgi be burgwar gudimargu,
\v 2 bemar we napneggi-igar-mamaidba nanadii gusmalad. Nia-saila-burbar-negsemaidba be ibmar-imakdii gusmalad. Emide, amba a-nia-saila-burba dulemar-yapa-Bab-Dummad-itomaladgi alamaknaid.
\p 
\v 3 Iduar anmar belagwapa, we-dulemaryob gudii gusmogad.
\p Anmar san-isguedbina-sogedba nanadii gusad.
\p Anmar e-itolegedba-ibmar-imakbiedba nanadii gusad.
\p Degine, anmar anmar-binsaedba ibmar-imakdii gusad.
\p Degisoggu, gusgu-anmar-daedba, baigan-Bab-Dummad-wissurmaladyob, anmar Bab-Dummadse sabsur-odurdaklemogoenad.
\p 
\v 4 Emigindi, Bab-Dummad, bela-bela wile anmar-daksoggu, nue dummarba anmar-sabgusad.
\v 5 Degisoggu, amba anmar isguedgi burgwar-gudigu, Bab-Dummad dula-Cristo-imaknonikidyob, dula anmar-imaknonimogad. Bab-Dummad anmar-abonoge-wilubsulinad, degite, anmar-abonononikid.
\p 
\v 6 Bab-Dummad Cristo-odulosadyob anmar-odulononimogad, degine, nibneggi Cristo-Jesúsʼba-sigega anmar-imaksad.
\v 7 Adi, yoedse-ibagan-danikoedgi mag daklegegar, Bab-Dummad anmargi nued binsaewilubsulinye. Emigindi, Cristo-Jesúsʼbali bela-bela nued anmargi-binsaedba anmar-bendaknoniye.
\p 
\v 8 Ar bemar abonolege-wilubsulinad, emigindi, Jesucristoʼgi-bensulidba Bab-Dummad bemar-abonononikid. Ar bemar na dukin Jesucristoʼgi abonoleged amissulid. Ar Bab-Dummad na e bemarga abonoleged-igar uksad.
\v 9 We-abonolegedi, na be ibmar-imakedgi abonolessulid, adi, bemar mer na san-dummarba imakmalagar.
\p 
\v 10 Bab-Dummad anmar-ogwanonikid. Cristo-Jesúsʼgi ibmar-nuegan-imakega anmar-ogwanonikid. Ar Bab-Dummad bato we-ibmar-nuegan iduar mesisad, adi, anmar a-ibmar-nuegan imakegar.
\s1 Jesúsʼgi, anmar soggwenna gunonikid
\p 
\v 11 Degisoggu be insamalo, be gwalulesmaladi, Judío-dulesur be gwalulesmalad. Judíoʼmar, abgan-uka-duku-sikarmaladye na dukin bimalad. Wemarde, abgan-uka-duku-sikarsurmaladye be-bismalad. We-abgan-uka-duku-siklegedi, dule-imakedid.
\v 12 Epennedi, bemar Cristo-wissuli gudigusmalad.
\p Bemar Israel-dulemargi-akanisurmalad. Degisoggu, Bab-Dummad-Israel-Dulemar-Ebo-Igar-Mesisad geg bemargadga gusundo.
\p We-napneggi Bab-Dummad-sate be gudigusmalad, degine, bendakleged-igar-sate be gudigusmarbalid.
\p 
\v 13 Iduardi, bemar Bab-Dummadgi dikasur-bangus gudigusmalad. Emigindi, bemar Cristo-Jesúsʼgi-bengusurmaladba, Bab-Dummad Cristo-e-abegi e-walikaa bemar-imaknonikid.
\p 
\v 14 Cristo anmarga gwage-bogidik-imakedsoggu, Judíoʼmar, degi, Judíoʼsurmaladbo oatononikid, neggwebur-unnila-soggwennagwadga imaknonikid. Igi na isdar-dakmaladba neg-abargi galu-emakmala, deyob galu-gwichid Cristo anmarga osulononikid.
\p 
\v 15 Cristo e-burgwisadgi isdar-dakmalad osulononikid.
\p Moisés-Igargi igar-sabsur-soglemamaid-e-gangued, degi, e-ibmar-imakleged-e-gangued, obelononikid.
\p Adi, Judíoʼmar, degi, Judíoʼsurmalad na-isdar-dakdimalad, Cristo na egi dulemar-binidga imaknonikid, degi, neggwebur-soggwennagwadga imaknonikid.
\v 16 Degine, Jesucristo nakrusgi-burgwisad-ular, neggwebur-gwabo, Judíoʼmar, degi, Judíoʼsurmalad na abin-abin-imakdigusmalad osulononikid. Neggwebur-gwagwenga imaknonikid. Cristo neggwebur-gwabobela Bab-Dummad-ebo ega igar-naboged imaksad.
\p 
\v 17 Cristo-nonikidi, Bab-Dummad-walikaa-gudimaladga, degi, Bab-Dummadgi-dikasur-bangus-gudimaladga Gayaburba-Nuedgi-sunmakega nonikid, dule-gwage-bogidik-saedgi-sunmakega nonikid.
\v 18 Ar Judíoʼmar, degi, Judíoʼsurmalad, bela anmar unnila Cristoʼginbi Bab-Dummad-Burba-Isligwaledba Babse-walikaguega anmar-imaksasunnad.
\p 
\v 19 Ar degisoggu, bar bemar, dule-ainebalidsulid, dule-yar-baidginedsurbalid. Bemar, bemar-iduar-Bab-Dummadgi-akananaimalad-yopiramarmogad, bemar Bab-Dummadgi gwenadgan-sunnadmarmogad.
\v 20 Bemar Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad, Jesús-e-sapingan-bur-dummagan-igar-odurdaksamaladgi, degi, Bab-Dummad-gayaburba-barsogmalad-igar-odurdaksamaladgi akwa-neg-sobaledyobi be gumaladid. A-igarmargi be negyob soblesmaladid. We-neg-soblesadi, Jesucristo e-akwasailaga gued.
\v 21 Ar Jesucristoʼgi, we-neg-Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad ise soblegar siid, degi, nasgumaibalid. Adi, anmar, Bab-Jesúsʼgi Bab-Dummadse-goled-neg-islidikidga guegar.
\v 22 Agi bemar, Cristoʼgi-akani, nue-soblemaimarmogad, adi, bela bemar neg-nuedga guegar. A-neggi Bab-Dummad na E-Burbabali anmargi megegar.
\c 3
\s1 Pablo, Judíoʼsurmaladga Bab-Gayaburba barsogedid
\p 
\v 1 Ani, Pablo, Cristo-Jesúsʼgi an sunmakdiidbali esgaryagi an mellesisunnad. Bemar-Judíoʼsurmaladga an nue-arbadiid. A-ulale, an anmar-Dummad-Jesucristo-e-Bab-asabinni, an yokorgi sindigar sigdiid.
\v 2 Ar bato bemar Bab-Dummad-anga-arbaed-uksad itosmalargebed, bemarga sogega, dulemar abonole-wilubsulinye, degite, Bab-Dummad nabir na e bemargi-binsaedba bemar-abonodaye.
\p 
\v 3 We-igar-dukuarmai-gusad, Bab-Dummad anse oyosad, igi bato iduar an bemarse bipisaar narmaksadyob.
\v 4 Ar an-bemarse-narmaksad be absodmalale, mag be itomaloed, bule an bannase Cristo-igar-dukuar-maid mag an itoge.
\v 5 We-Bab-Jesús-igar-dukuarmai-gusad, dulemar-iduar-ambikusmaladgardi gwen osanaloledsulid. Emigindi, we-igar-dukuarmai-gusad, Bab-Dummad-Burbaba Jesús-e-sapingan-bur-dummagan gwage-swilidikmaladga, degi, e-gayaburba-barsogmaladga osanalolesad.
\p 
\v 6 We-igar-dukuarmai-gusad, wedo:
\p Dulemar-Judíoʼsurmalad Bab-Jesúsʼgi-bensulidba Gayaburba-Nued-abingasadgi, Judíoʼmarba-mesa Bab-Dummad-ibmar abingamogoed. Amar san-wargwennayob gunonikid, degi, Bab-Dummad Israel-dulemarga-ibmar-ukoye-sogsad Cristo-Jesúsʼgi egadga gunonimogad.
\p 
\v 7 We-Gayaburba-Nuedgi an sunmakewilubsulinad. Ar emigindi, Bab-Dummad, nabir-e-angi-binsasadba, e-gangued-angi-arbasadba, a-ulale, E-Gayaburba-Nuedgi-sunmakega an-nug-imaksad.
\v 8 Ar an-bur Jesucristoʼba-nanaimaladba bur-bipi-inigwele, degite, Bab-Dummad, Judíoʼsurmaladga E-Gayaburba-Nued-Cristoʼgi-soglesadgi-an-sunmakega an-susad. We-Cristo-igar, bur igar-nuedid, dulemar bela-mag-itogosulid-igalad.
\p 
\v 9 Degine, belagwapa dulemar-baiganga-oyogega anga igar uklesad. We-igar, Bab-Dummad-bela-we-napneg-naidgi-ibmar-urbisadbi iduar wisi mainad. Emigindi, Cristoʼgi magar itolenonisunnad.
\v 10 Adi, emigindi, Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-ambikunonidamaladba nibneggi-burbar-dummaganga-gumaid, degine, nibneggi-burbar-gandikidba-gangued-nikmalad, Bab-Dummad-e-binsaed-dummarba-nikad wisgumalagar.
\p 
\v 11 Ar gusgu Bab-Dummad na weyob igar-mesisadi, anmar-Dummad-Cristo-Jesúsʼgi bela ibmar imaksad.
\v 12 Emigindi, Cristo-ibmar-imaksadba, degine, Cristoʼgi anmar nue-bensulidba, anmar Bab-Dummadse dobsuli nabir ese dogsunnad.
\v 13 Degisoggu, a-ular, an bemarga sogmarsun, an Bab-Jesús-Igargi bemar-ular-wiledimar-inigwele, mer galakumalo. Ar ade, an bemar-ular-wilediidbali be-nug ogannoledimalad.
\s1 Jesucristo-sabed bur dummarbad
\p 
\v 14 A-ulale, anmar-Dummad-Jesucristo-e-Bab-asabinni an yokorgi sindigar sigsunnad,
\v 15 ar ade, bela dulemar akar-akar-nibneggi-bukmalad, degi, napneggi-bukmalad Bab-Dummadgi nug nikunonidaed.
\p 
\v 16 An Bab-Dummadse egissun, e-gangued-dummarba-nikadba, bemarga e-gangued ukegar. Adi, bemar ulubgi, E-Burbagi ganguegar.
\v 17 Adi, bemar ulubgi Cristo-bensulidba, Cristo bemar-gwagegi megegar.
\p An Bab-Dummadse bemarga egisbar, ar bela-bela-sabguedgi ise-diglegaledgi,
\v 18 bemar bela dulemar-Jesucristoʼgi-akananaimaladba Cristo-sabgued ise mag itoar-gumarmogarsun.
\p Bule Cristo-sabgued matardungue, bule sugubali, bule wilasailabali, degine, bule nibgubali.
\p 
\v 19 Deginbali, Cristo-sabgued-dule-geg-bela-wisguedi, a bemar magar-itogemarsun, adi, Bab-Dummad bela-bela bemargi gudii guegar.
\p 
\v 20 Emigindi, Bab-Dummad e-gangued-anmargi-arbanaidba, anmar ese ibmar-egised, anmar-ibmar-mag-itoged, bur bule nabir anmarga ibmar imaked.
\v 21 A-ular, Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-ambikunonidamaladba Cristo-Jesúsʼgi, degisadegu, Bab-Dummad-nug odummoledii gusun. Ar deyobdo.
\c 4
\ms1 3. BAB-JESÚSʼBA-NANAIMALAD-E-DAED
\mr (4:1–6:20)
\s1 Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad bulakwaa nanaewilubmalad
\p 
\v 1 Ani Pablo, Bab-Jesús-nug-ular, an esgaryagi-mellesiid-duled, an bemarse ise-wilesakwaa egismar, be nue nanamar.
\p Ar igi Bab-mimmigan nanaewilubmala, deyob be nanamar.
\p 
\v 2 Bipisaale mer be san-dummarba na be imakmalo.
\p Binnalegwadgi be ibmar imakmarbalo.
\p Melle be itosur sae-itomalo.
\p Na be sabmaladgi, nossurmaladyob be muchub-muchub dakmalo.
\p 
\v 3 Bab-Dummad-Burbagi ulubgi-bogidikidgi be alamaknai imakmar, adi, na be danakwaa gudii gumalagar.
\p 
\v 4 Unnila Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad san wargwennaa gued, degi, Bab-Dummad-Burba wargwennaa gubalid.
\p Degine, Bab-Dummad, abonoleged-igar-soggwennaa-maid-nikuega bemarse gochad.
\p 
\v 5 Unnila Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-e-Dummad wargwennaa gued.
\p Akar-akar-Jesúsʼgi-bensuliguled sated.
\p Bab-Jesús-diigi-ogleged-igar gwennaa gubalid.
\p 
\v 6 Bab-Dummad unnila wargwennaa gued. A-Bab-Dummad bela dulemar-e-babad.
\p A-Bab-Dummad belagwapa dulemargi negsemaid, a bela dulemargi arbanaibalid, degi, bela dulemarba gudibalid.
\p 
\v 7 Degi-inigwele, Cristo nabir-anmargi-binsaedba na e-itolegedba, igi-mergu-gurgin-ukbiedba bela anmarga akar-akar uksad.
\p 
\v 8 Degisoggu, a-ular, Bab-Dummad-Garda wegi-soged:
\q1 “Nibnegse nakwisgu, dule-galesmalad eba sesad,
\q2 Dulemarga gurgin-nuegan uksad.”
\qr Salmo 68:18
\p 
\v 9 (¿Ar wede, ibi obarsunna, nibnegse nakwisye? A sogledo, Jesús napase aidesye.
\v 10 Ar dule-aidesadi, amba e-sunnad niba nakwisbardo, adi, bela niba, degi, napneggi, neg-gaegar.)
\p 
\v 11 Bab-Jesús-sunnad na e-sordamarga akar-akar gurgin uksad.
\p Gwenna-gwenna E-sapingan-bur-dummaganga nug-imaksad.
\p Baigandi, Bab-gayaburba-barsogedga nug-imaksad.
\p Baigan, Bab-Jesúsʼgi-Abonoleged-Igargi-sunmakega nug-imaksad.
\p Degi, baigan Bab-Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-iduedga, degi, Jesús-igargi dule-bamalad-odurdakega nug-imaksad.
\p 
\v 12 Wemar Jesucristoʼgi-akananaimalad-odurdaksad, adi, Bab-Jesúsʼga arbaegar, degi, gatik Bab-Jesús-igargi nasgumai guegar.
\p 
\v 13 Degidbali, bela anmar na danakwaa wargwennayob Cristoʼgi-bensuli gumalagar, degine, Bab-Dummad-Machi-gatik-nue-magar-dake gumarbaligar.
\p Anmar Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad, nue-nasgumai Cristoʼyobidse gumalagar.
\p 
\v 14 Deyob anmar gusale, anmar bar mimmigan-baisursunna-binsaed-galegedyob guosulid. Anmar baisursunna igar-baiganse binsaed-galedii guosulid, eba ebipiledii guosulid.
\p Adi, anmar dulemar-emar-yardakmaladse, yamo-binsaed-nikadyob-sunmakmaladse, mer baisursunna binsaed-galedii gumalagar.
\v 15 Unnila anmar sabedgine, igar-napiragwadgi-nadapi, nue bela ibmar-nuegangi, Cristoʼgi-nasgumai gumalagar. Ar Cristo bela Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-e-sailaga gusiid.
\p 
\v 16 Ar anmar Cristo-sanyob-gumarsoggu, Cristo anmarga war-wargwen-arbaed-uksadbali, egi-akaega anmar-imaked. Degine, bela war-wargwengi na muchub-muchub bulakwa-arbaega anmar-imaked. Adi, bela Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad sabguedgi nasgumai-nasgumai guega, degi, bela-bela gangumai-gangumai gubaligar.
\s1 Jesús-igargi-nanaega epennegwad-igar be metemar
\p 
\v 17 We an bemarga soged, Bab-Jesúsʼgi weyob abeleged:
\p Mer be dulemar-Bab-Dummad-wissurmaladyob bar damalo. Ar amardi, binsaed-isganagi gudimalad.
\p 
\v 18 Ar amardi, e-binsaedgi galagwensuli gudimalad. Bab-Dummadgi-dula-gudigued gwen niksurmalad.
\p Amar yapa Bab-Dummadba-ibsamaladba, a-igar-wissuli gudimalad. Deyob gudimarsunnad.
\p 
\v 19 A-dulemar gwen bar binge itosurmalad. Isguedga na san urmaksa gudimarsunnad. Bela ibmar-sunnasur-imakdimaladgi na wergudimarsunnad.
\p 
\v 20 Ar bemardi wegi-galagwensulidaedi, ar Cristoʼgi be gwen deyob durdaksasurmalad.
\p 
\v 21 Ar bemardi nue Cristo-igar itosmalad. Ar nue Cristo-igargi bemar odurdaklesmalad, degi, igar-napiragwad Jesúsʼgi-maidba be odurdaklesmarbalid.
\p 
\v 22 Epenne be igar-seredba-nanadigusad, be metemarsun. Ar a-igardi bato isgus maid, unnila dulemar-yardakedgi binsamaid.
\v 23 Degisoggu, be binsaed obinomarsun.
\v 24 Degi, be igar-nuegan sumarsun, adi, dule-gwapidga be gumalagar. Ar Bab-Dummad na eyob bemar-obinnisad, adi, igar-napiragwadgi, degi, gwage-swilidikidgi be innikii nanamalagar.
\p 
\v 25 Degisoggu, be gakansaed mimarsun, unnila be igar-napiragwadgi na ga be sunmakmarsun, ar ade, anmar bela Cristoʼgi unnila san-wargwennaa gumalad.
\p 
\v 26 Be urwele, mer we-urwed isguega be-imakega be sao. Degine, be ulusale, mer egi be bar binsadii sao. Ulusar, abga ies be imako.
\v 27 Adi, mer nia-sailaga be-san be ukegar.
\p 
\v 28 Ar dule ibmar-atursaerbale, mer bar ibmar-atursao. Emigindi, arbao, adi, e-arbaedgi, dulemar-baigan-ibmar-abedimaladga sunna ibmar-ukmogoed.
\p 
\v 29 Gaya-isgana mer be sunmako. Unnila be gaya-nueganbi-sunmako, adi, nabir be dule-baigan-ogannogega, baigan-be-itobukmalad yeer-ito be imakegar.
\v 30 Mer Bab-Dummad-Burba-Isligwaled bukib-binsaed be imakmar, ar Bab-Dummad-Burba-Isligwaled wilubga bemargi nagunonikid, adi, Bab-Dummad bela-isguedgi-bemar-onogoed-ibaganse bemar mag daklemalagar, be Cristoʼgad gumalad.
\q2 
\v 31 Bemargi, bela isdar-itoged,
\q2 sae-itoged, urwed-naid,
\q2 binnasur-aimarse-urwed,
\q2 dulemar-ukabsaed,
\q2 degine, bela isdar-binsaedgi-ibmar-imaked, osulomarsun.
\p 
\v 32 Unnila na be yeer-itogedgi muchub-muchub bendakmar, na be wile dakmar. Degi, na egi be warmaksamalale, ar igi-Bab-Dummad be-isgusad Cristoʼgi bega-osulosmoga, deyob ies na be imakmarmo.
\c 5
\s1 Bemar Bab-Dummad-mimmigan gwallu-meegwad gumalad
\p 
\v 1 Degisoggu, bemar Bab-Dummad-mimmigan-sabesailadmarsoggu, Bab-Dummad-daedba be damarsun.
\v 2 Degi, sabguedgi be nanamar, ar igi Cristo anmar-sabgusmoga, degine, ise-wawadik Bab-Dummadga ibmar-ogumakar-uklegedyob anmar-ular na e-san uksamoga, ayob be nanamar.
\p 
\v 3 Ar bemar Jesucristoʼgi be akananaimarsoggu, bipisaale, bemargi we-ibmar soglegewilubsulid:
\q2 Abirgunagwarsuli negsichigi-nanaleged,
\q2 galagwensuli-nanaleged-igar,
\q2 ibmarbina surbinsa-itoleged-igar.
\p 
\v 4 Deginbali, melle weyob be sunmako:
\q2 Gaya-isganase-bakale, mer egi be sunmakmar,
\q2 mer binsa galagwensuli be sunmakmar,
\q2 mer sunnasur gaya-isganagi-sunmaklemaladgi be sunmakmar.
\q3 Suli, we-gaya-degimalad, ibnuedsulid. Bur Bab-Dummadga dog-nuedye, be sogmar.
\p 
\v 5 Ar bato bemar wisid, dule abirgunagwarsuli-na-negsichigi-yolediidi, dule galagwensuli-gudiidi, degi, dule dogdar-ibmarbina-surbinsa-itodiidi, (we-ibmar e-bab-dummadga na imakdiid), Cristo-negdakmaidse, degi, Bab-Dummad-e-negdakmaidse, doged-igar ega gwen maisulid.
\p 
\v 6 Mer dulemar-emar-binsaed-gaega yogasaar-sunmakmaladse be yardaklemalo. Ar Bab-Dummad, eba-dasurmalad galagwensulidaedbali, sabsur-odurdakdedaed.
\v 7 Degisoggu, amar-degidamaladbali, mer eba ibmar-isgana be imakmar.
\p 
\v 8 Ar epennedi, bemar negsichigi galagwensuli gudigusmalanad. Ar emigindi, bemar, Bab-Jesúsʼgi neg-meegwadgi gudimalad. Degisoggu, Bab-Dummad-mag-daked-dule na be san oyomar,
\v 9 (ar Bab-Dummad-mag-daked-dule weyob daed: Bela igar-nuegangi nanae, igar-innikigwadbi imake, degine, igar-napiragwadbi sae),
\v 10 degi, be durdakbarmarsun, igid-igar Bab-Jesús-nabir-ito imakedi.
\p 
\v 11 Mer ibmar-isgana-negsichidgi-imaklemalad be imakmar. Dulemar-deyob-ibmar-imakmaladga bur be oyoge, emarde nue nodimarye.
\v 12 Ar ade, bemar we-dulemar-ibmar-isgana-dukuar-imakdiidgi-sunmakedbela ibnuedsulid, agi be sunmaked be binge-itogewilubbid.
\v 13 Ar bela ibmar gwallu-meegwadse onolesale, mag dakledaed, we-ibmar ibmar-isganamarye. Ar gwallu bela ibmar-mag-dakle imaked.
\v 14 Ar a-ulale, sogleged:
\q1 “Be gabmaid, ataksun,
\q2 dulemar-burgwarmalad-abargi be gwisgusun,
\q2 degi, Cristo gwallu-meegwadga bega gunonisunnoed.”
\p 
\v 15 Degisoggu, be-daedgine nue be nanamarsun, melle dule-ibmar-wissurmaladyob be damar, dule-nue-ibmar-wisidyob be nanamarsun.
\v 16 Ibagan-nagumaidgi nue egi be gudii imakmar, ar ibagan-isganade bukidargusad.
\p 
\v 17 Degisoggu, melle binsaedsuli be nanamar. Aka bur be Bab-Jesús igi-nanabi bemar-abemai, a bur be imakdii gumar.
\p 
\v 18 Degine, melle be mumgumar. Ar mumguedi, galagwensuli dule-onanae imaked. Bur bela-bela Bab-Dummad-Burba-Isligwaledse-seledii na be imakmar.
\q2 
\v 19 Na be muchub-muchub salmosʼgi namakmar.
\q2 Bab-Dummad-nug-odummoged-namaklegedgi be namakmar,
\q2 burba-ogannoged-namaklegedgi be namakdii imakmar,
\q2 degi, Bab-Jesús-nug ogannodii be-gwagegi be imakmarsun.
\q2 
\v 20 Anmar-Bab-Jesucristo-nuggi, Bab-Dummad-anmar-babga, bela dogdar-nuedye sogdigu be imakmarsun.
\q2 
\v 21 Bab-Dummad-dobekwaa-nanaedgi na be muchub-muchub urbaligwa-nanadii gumalo.
\s1 Ome sui-urbaligwa nanaoed, degi, sui nue ome-sabgumogoed
\p 
\v 22 Omegan-sui-nikmalad, na be-sui-urbaligwa nanamar. Igi Bab-Jesús-urbalikwaa be nanadimala, deyob be-sui-urbaligwa be nanamar.
\v 23 Ar sui, ome-e-dummadga gued. Deyobi, Cristo na eba-nanaimalad-e-dummadga gumogad. Degi, Cristo, eba-nanaimalad-e-Abonogedga gubalid. Degisoggu, Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad, Cristo-e-sanga gusiid.
\v 24 Degisoggu, ar igi Cristoʼba-nanaimalad Cristo-sogedba nanadii, debayobi omegan e-sui-urbaligwa bela nanamogoed.
\p 
\v 25 Ar igi Cristo na eba-nanaimalad-sabgusa, degine, Bab-Dummadgadga-imakega eba-nanaimaladbina-burgwisa, deyobi, machergan, be-ome na be sabgumar.
\v 26 Ar Cristo, deyob eba-nanaimalad E-Gayaburba-sogedba, degi, Bab-diigi-ogleged-igar-imaklegedba swilidik imaksad.
\v 27 Adi, Cristo, eba-nanaimalad nue-swilidikidgi, isgued-naisulidgi, bela yeerdaklege, gwen gutu-naisuli, bapi-bapidsuli, bela nued-daklege, deyob na ega-ukega, na eba-nanaimalad-imaksad.
\p 
\v 28 Ar sui, igi Cristo na eba-nanaimalad-sabgue, deyob, na e-ome-sabgumogargebed. Ar sui, igi na e-san sabgue, deyob, na e-ome-sabgumogo. Ar dule na e-ome-sabele, dukin na e-san sabgued.
\v 29 Ar dule bipisaale e-san geg na isdardaked, bur bule e-san na nued akwed, degi, nue na masgi ogunbalid. Ar deyob, Cristo na eba-nanaimalad-imakmogad.
\v 30 Ar ade, anmar Cristo-e-san-mesadid. Anmar, e-san gued, degi, e-galagan gued.
\q1 
\v 31 “A-ulale, machered e-babgi bangudoed,
\q2 e-nangi bangudoed.
\q1 Geb machered e-ome-ebo garmakdii guoed.
\q2 Ebogwadi, san-wargwennagwadga gunonikoed.”
\qr Génesis 2:24
\p 
\v 32 We wargwenna-gunonidaedi, igar-dummadid, nue aku itolegedid. We degi-an-sogedi, Cristo, degine, na eba-nanaimalad-ebo-igar-maidgi an deyob soged.
\p 
\v 33 Degisoggu, bemar na wala-walagwen, ar igi na-be-san-sabmala, deyob na-be be-ome sabgumogoed. Degine, ome, e-suigi binsaed-nikaa nanadii guoed.
\c 6
\s1 Mimmigan-ebo nued-nanamalad-igar
\p 
\v 1 Mimmigan, Bab-Jesús-nuggine, nue be-babganba uaya-nikaa be damalo, ar we, igar-nuedid.
\q1 
\v 2 “Be-babba, degine, be-nanba be ibsadii nanamalo.”
\qr Deuteronomio 5:16a
\p Ar we bur igar-sunsogedid. Agi Bab-Dummad anmarga sogsad:
\q1 “Weba be damalale, ibmar-nued an bega ukoye.
\q2 
\v 3 Adi, bemarga bela igar-nueganbi naegar,
\q2 degine, adi, we-napneggine bemar sereddii megegar.”
\qr Deuteronomio 5:16b
\p 
\v 4 Degine, babgan, bemarmoga, mer binsa be-mimmigan-ourwed be sao. Suli, degisuli. Bur be Bab-Dummad-urbaligwa-nanaedgi be odurdako, degine, Bab-Dummad-igar-nuedgi-unadii be imako.
\s1 Maigan, degi, dummagan, igi-damalargebe
\p 
\v 5 Maigan, bemar be-dummagan-we-napnegginmaladgi nue eba be uaya-nikaa damalo, dobekwaa egi be gudimalo. Mer egi be isdaradgi-gudii gumalo, egi-nued-binsaedgi be damalo, Cristoʼga-arbanaiyob be imakmalo.
\v 6 Be nue arbamar. Mer be be-dummad-be-dakdiidginbi arbamalo, be ega oyogega be nued arbamar-dakleye. Ar bemar Cristo-maiga-gusoggu, Bab-Dummad-sogedba be nue ulubgi ise-arbaar imakmar.
\p 
\v 7 Bemar nue weligwar ulubgi ise-arbaar be imakmar. Bab-Jesúsʼga-arbanaiyob be imakmar, dulemarga arbanaisuliyob be imakmar.
\v 8 Ar be nue-wismalad, be maiga-gudiidgindibe, maiga-gudiidginsurdibe, gwenna-gwenna be ibmar-nued-imaksadba, Bab-Jesús bemar-bennukoed.
\p 
\v 9 Degine, dummagan, bemarmoga, be mai-nikmalad, bemar be-maigan be nue akwemarmogo, mer be be-mai-sabsur-imakmalo. Nue be insamalo, bemala, degi, be-maigan, dummad-wargwenna nikamalad. We-bemar-Dummadi, nibneggi maid. A-Dule-Dummadi bela emarbi dulemar-dakmaid.
\s1 Burbar-urwedgi ibmar-ebulemalad
\p 
\v 10 Emigindi gwenadgan, Bab-Jesúsʼgi gandik be akamar. Cristo-e-ganguedgi gatik be gangumai gumarsun.
\v 11 Igi sordamar urwenasokalir, urwed-mor yosdamala, deyob Bab-Dummad-e-gangued-burbaled-uked be yomar, adi, nia-saila bemar-yardakarsogele, bemar nia-saila-abin ganna gwisguegar.\fig Romano-sordamar urwenasokalir, urwed-mor yosdamalad. (Efesios 6:10-17) |src="LB00196B.TIF" size="col" ref="Efesios 6:11"\fig*
\q2 
\v 12 Ar anmar dulemarbo urwenanaisurmalad,
\q2 burba-gandikidba-gangued-nikmaladbo urwenaid,
\q2 anmar burba-isgana-dummaganga-gumamaidbo urwenaid,
\q2 we-napnegsichidnaid-isganamar-semamaid-e-dummaganbo urwenaid,
\q2 degine, niba niamar-e-dummagan-gudimaladbo anmar urwenaid.
\p 
\v 13 Degisoggu, a-ulale, bemar Bab-Dummad-e-gangued-uked-e-mor-burbaled be yomarsun, adi, bemar ibagan-isganagi nabir bela ulusad-sorba amba gandik gwichi guegar.
\p 
\v 14 Degisoggu, be gandik gwisgumar. Nue salakarmar. Ar igi sordamar urwed-idu guakwaa gudiguegala, e-saderba molidub-nasikdamala, deyob be Bab-Dummad-igar-napiragwad-wisidba be guakwaa gudigumar. Mer nailikguega, igi sordamar na binasgargi arsoged yodamala, deyob be igar-innikigwadgi nanamar.
\v 15 Ar igi sordamar bato naegala, guakwaa sapat-yoi gudidae, deyob be Bab-Gayaburba-Nued-gwage-bogidik-saed-barsogega, be guakwaa gudisamar.
\v 16 Ar igi sordamar na e-sigu-abgaedgi dukue, deyob be Jesucristoʼgi napiragwadgi-bensuli be nanamar. Adi, sunna bemar sigu-gwabunyearmalad nia-saila-miedi, oginnegar.
\v 17 Igi sordamar nono-arsogega bormo-gurgin e-nonogi-sii dae, deyobi abonoleged-igargi be nanadii imako. Degine, nia-abinsaega, Bab-Dummad-Burba-e-es-suid be sue. We-es-suid an bega sogedi, Bab-Dummad-e-gayaburba gued.
\p 
\v 18 Bab-Dummad-Burbaba bela-bela be Bab-Dummadse gordii imako. Babse-akar-akar-gorlegedgi, degine, bela ese ibmar-egisedgi be Bab-Dummadse gole. Be guagwar gudii imakmar, degine, bela Jesucristoʼgi-akananaimaladga Bab-Dummadse be gordigu imakmar.
\p 
\v 19 Degine, be anga Bab-Dummadse gormarmogo, adi, Bab-Dummad-Igargi an sunmakdele, Bab-Dummad anga an-ibmar-soged ukegar, degine, an dobsuli e-Gayaburba-dule-sunna-abonoged-epenne-dukuar-maigusadgi an sunmakegar.
\v 20 Ar ade, Bab-Dummad-nuggi-an-sunmakdiid-ular an esgoro-dubgi emi an edilles mellesisunnad. Anga Bab-Dummadse gatik gormalo, adi, an dobsuli we-Gayaburbagi an sunmakegar. Ar deyob an dobsuli sunmakergebed.
\ms1 4. NAPI-SOGLENAID
\mr (6:21-24)
\s1 Pablo, we-garda-narmaksiidgi napi ibmar sogsad
\p 
\v 21 Tíquico, anmar-gwenad-sabed, degi, Bab-Jesúsʼga-arbadiid-dule, a-dule, gwen galakudisulid, a bemarga sognadapoed, igi an gudii, degine, ibimar an imaknaibali.
\v 22 Ar a-ulale, an bemarse Tíquico-barminaid, adi, be wisgumalaga igi anmar gudidii, degine, adi, bemar-gwage-ogannomalagarbar.
\p 
\v 23 Gwenadgan, Bab-Dummad-anmar-babga-gumaid, degi, Bab-Jesucristo, ulubgi bogidik bemar-ito imaksun. Degine, sabgued, degi, egi bensulid, bemarga ukbarsun.
\v 24 Deginbali, Bab-Dummad bela-anmar-Dummad-Jesucristo-nue-sabmaladgi nued binsasun.
